headline: Buying the Dip: 3 Super Safe High-Yield Dividend Stocks I Added to My Retirement Account During the Stock Market Sell-Off.
summary: The stock market recently took a big dip, driven down by concerns about how much tariffs will affect the economy.  One of the benefits of falling stock prices is that dividend yields move in the opposite direction.
